      <h2>Transparency First</h2>
      <p>At AICommandDesk, we believe in complete transparency with our readers. Some of the links on this website are affiliate links, which means we may earn a commission if you click on the link or make a purchase using the link.</p>

      <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>No extra cost</strong> — You will never pay more because of an affiliate link. The price is the same whether you use our link or go directly to the vendor.</li>
