      <p>We may earn affiliate commissions from:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI tools and software</li>
        <li>Productivity and SaaS products</li>
        <li>Online courses and educational platforms</li>
        <li>Hosting and web services</li>
        <li>Books and digital resources</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Promise</h2>
      <p>We will always prioritize your trust over any commission. If a product is bad, we will say so — even if we could earn money by recommending it. Your success is what builds our long-term success.</p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
